	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">NORMAL PAD CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor & select command:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Confirms command or selects tile:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancels command or tile; switches help and back display on/off if no tile selected:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Switches viewpoint when pressed at same tiem as a directional button (classic shanghai mode only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Speeds up cursor movement (rolling shanghai mode only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate the tile cube to the left (rolling shanghai mode only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate the tile cube to the right (rolling shanghai mode only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Starts game; pauses; opens and closes menu window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MOUSE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Mouse</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Confirms command or selects tile:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Changes viewpoint (classic shanghai mode only):
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left Button (Hold)</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancels command or tile; switches help and back display on/off if no tile selected:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Right Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Starts game; pauses; opens and closes menu window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Left Button (Double click)</font><br><br>
     &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
